text = "The controls are quite simple:

Press WASD to Move
Press Space to Jump
Press Shift to Dash. Your dash meter will refil while you are grounded
and while you run on walls
Press CTRL to Crouch. If you have enough speed, you can Slide as well
Press Q to quickly turn around

And that is it!
Have fun and may the winds guide you."
font_size = 100
outline_size = 20
autowrap_trim_flags = 64

